# obsidian-mcp service env - resolved by op-wrap.sh at launchd startup.
# References only, never values (secrets-as-references rule).
#
# This server authenticates clients via OAuth 2.1 (FastMCP native auth), NOT a
# static bearer - it reads no `*_AUTH_TOKEN` from the environment. No op:// refs
# are required here. (A stray `MAC_MCP_AUTH_TOKEN` ref lived here historically and
# was injected-but-ignored; removed 2026-06-23 as vestigial - see credentials-map changelog.)
